{"tid":1884321,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰國新增一起新冠肺炎確診病例：來自中國，一家九口全部確診","createTime":"2020-02-17T13:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T17:34:33.000Z","uid":85180,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"48c79eea6b083d95d2dfbd2d8769325a95f05851","tid":1884321,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:51:50.000Z","msg":"泰國新增一起新冠肺炎確診病例：來自中國，一家九口全部確診<br />\n<br />\n新加坡聯合早報消息，泰國周一（17日）新增一起新冠肺炎確診病例，患者為一名60歲中國籍女子。此外，泰國也加強了對新加坡和日本入境者的冠病檢查。<br />\n<br />\n泰國衛生部常務次長蘇康在記者會上說，這名60歲中國籍婦女是之前確診病患的家屬。該婦女確診後，她們一家九口所有人都確診患上冠病。<br />\n<br />\n泰國目前的確診病例達35起，其中有15人已康復出院，另外20人還在醫院接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28fe527e1d875d02acb0dd13d1548f20f4bd086","tid":1884321,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支那肺炎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n秦國都係抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87260faab88ded8a59bddaafa6c282793e966a34","tid":1884321,"uid":21699,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T13:55:03.000Z","msg":"投票<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一宗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一起"},{"pid":"289fa22ba44f910e0d305513c65761267071edc9","tid":1884321,"uid":185045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T14:12:06.000Z","msg":"呢個支那家庭名乎其實冚家鏟"},{"pid":"a5154bcc3e38f9eb09166c48287fc1116229013c","tid":1884321,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco